'''Otto Schneider-Orelli''' (10 August 1880 in [[Münchenbuchsee]] &ndash; 31 October 1965 in [[Zürich]]) was a Swiss [[entomologist]].
He studied natural sciences at the universities of [[University of Neuchâtel|Neuchâtel]] (1899) and [[University of Bern|Bern]] (1900–05). Following graduation, he worked as an assistant under [[Hermann Müller (Thurgau)|Hermann Müller-Thurgau]] at the research institute for [[arboriculture]], [[horticulture]] and [[viticulture]] in [[Wädenswil]], where from 1913, he worked as an entomologist. From 1928 to 1950 he served as an associate professor of entomology at [[ETH Zurich]] and as director of the Institute of Entomology.<ref name=SV>[http://www.herbarien.uzh.ch/static/database/sammlerdetails_de.php?id=5252 Otto Schneider-Orelli] Zürcher Herbarien</ref><ref name=SU>[http://www.hls-dhs-dss.ch/textes/f/F31258.php?topdf=1 Schneider -Orelli, Otto] Dictionnaire historique de la Suisse</ref>
From 1917 onward, he was curator of collections at the entomology museum of ETH Zurich.<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=0-hrRQvGV7sC&pg=PA62&lpg=PA62&dq=%22Schneider-Orelli,+Otto%22+1879&source=bl&ots=3rdThcme57&sig=EbpGNqCoBRpUEBJweHZ5oCjOdmE&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjthdSk98nNAhUI4oMKHTvFAY4Q6AEIIzAC#v=onepage&q=%22Schneider-Orelli%2C%20Otto%22%201879&f=false Schmidt - Theyer / edited by Walther Killy] Dictionary of German Biography</ref> He specialized in the fields of agricultural and forest entomology. He was the author of many treatises on [[phylloxera]].<ref name=SV/><ref name=SU/>
== Selected works == * ''Reblausversuche im Kanton Zürich'', 1921 &ndash; Essay on phylloxera concerning the [[canton of Zürich]]. * ''Die Reblaus und unser Weinbau'', 1923 &ndash; Phylloxera and viticulture. * ''Vergleichende Untersuchungen zur Reblausfrage'' (with Hans Leuzinger), 1924 &ndash; Comparative studies on phylloxera. * ''Schädlingsbüchlein für Landwirtschaft, Garten, Haus und Hof'', 1938 &ndash; "Pest booklet" for farming, gardening, home and yard. * ''Entomologisches Praktikum; Einführung in die land- und forstwirtschaftliche Insektenkunde'', 1947 &ndash; Entomological internship; introduction to agricultural and forest entomology.<ref>[http://www.worldcat.org/search?q=au%3ASchneider-Orelli%2C+Otto%2C&qt=hot_author OCLC WorldCat Search] published works</ref> {{Botanist|Schneid.-Or.|Schneider-Orelli, Otto}}
