{{Redirect|First Lady of the World|the subject of Muller's book who had the nickname "First Lady of the World"|Eleanor Roosevelt}}
{{Infobox person
| name = Robert Muller
| birth_date = {{birth date|1923|03|11}}
| birth_place = [[Weismes]], Belgium
| death_date= {{death date and age|mf=yes|2010|09|20|1923|03|11}}
